OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy day, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of mostly light rain. Rain
OL,7,Fmay turn briefly heavy and showery
OL,8,Fthrough the middle of the day. Light
OL,9,Fwinds. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining largely cloudy
OL,12,Fthrough the evening, as rain gradually
OL,13,Fclears eastward. Becoming dry and
OL,14,Frather cold through the early hours,
OL,15,Fas cloud breaks. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
